OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,FLabour have announced the leader of
OL,7,FManchester City Council will be its
OL,8,Fcandidate in the city's forthcoming
OL,9,Fmayoral by-election.
OL,11,FThe vote will choose a new metro mayor
OL,12,Ffor the city region - a position which
OL,13,Fwas vacated when Number 10 hopeful
OL,14,FAndy Burnham was elected as the new MP
OL,15,Ffor Makerfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
