OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,FThe party says Cllr Craig, who is also
OL,7,Fthe Deputy Mayor for Economy, Business
OL,8,Fand Inclusive Growth for Greater
OL,9,FManchester, promises to set out a
OL,10,F"bold vision to build on the progress
OL,11,Fmade over the last decade and deliver
OL,12,Fthe next chapter for the region".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
