OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,FAnnouncing her candidacy, she said: "I
OL,7,Fwill work every day for us to make
OL,8,Fsure everyone shares in the success
OL,9,FGreater Manchester is building `
OL,10,Fmaking sure there's more money in
OL,11,Fpeople's pockets, pride in every town
OL,12,Fcentre with a New High Streets Fund, a
OL,13,Fnew generation of council and
OL,14,Faffordable homes and an expanded Bee
OL,15,FNetwork that freezes fares and that
OL,16,Fworks for all of us."
OL,18,FLabour described their candidate as a
OL,19,F"former council estate kid whose
OL,20,Ffamily endured unemployment, ill
OL,21,Fhealth and financial hardship."
OL,26,@nD@eOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
