OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,FCllr Craig said Greater Manchester
OL,7,Ftransformed her life after moving to
OL,8,Fthe city region when she was 18.
OL,10,FShe described it as a "special place"
OL,11,Fwhich has always "fought for progress"
OL,12,Fand paid tribute to the former mayor.
OL,14,F"While Westminster left places like
OL,15,Fours behind, Greater Manchester has
OL,16,Ftaken control of our own future and
OL,17,Fwe've started building our own success.
OL,26,@rD@WOUrD@eO]sD@ROUsD@fO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
