PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782236889
OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,F"Working alongside former Mayor Andy
OL,7,FBurnham, we have achieved so much over
OL,8,Fthe ` bringing buses back under public
OL,9,Fcontrol, creating jobs, attracting
OL,10,Finvestment, and pushing Greater
OL,11,FManchester forward as a real
OL,12,Fpowerhouse of the North West.
OL,14,F"But for too many people, who work
OL,15,Fhard and do the right thing, life
OL,16,Fstill feels too hard and unaffordable.
OL,17,FAs Mayor I will apply a simple test:
OL,18,Fwill it make life better?
OL,26,@nD@AOU
