OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,FCllr Craig became the first female
OL,7,Fleader of the city council in 2021 and
OL,8,Fis its first LGBT leader.
OL,10,FLabour said that she had a strong
OL,11,Frecord of delivery at a local
OL,12,Fgovernment level, citing a reduction
OL,13,Fin homelessness, overseeing council
OL,14,Fand affordable housebuilding and
OL,15,Fsupporting families through the cost
OL,16,Fof living crisis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
