PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782236889
OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,FIn a statement, the party added, "As
OL,7,Flead for Economy, Business and
OL,8,FInclusive Growth she's spearheaded the
OL,9,FGood Growth Fund and worked on Mayoral
OL,10,FDevelopment Corporations for towns and
OL,11,Fareas across Greater Manchester from
OL,12,FAtom Valley to Old Trafford to help
OL,13,Fcreate tens of thousands of jobs, or
OL,14,Frevitalise town centres like
OL,15,FMiddleton, Prestwich and Stockport."
OL,17,FLabour's deadline for nominations
OL,18,Fpassed on Tuesday, when Cllr Craig's
OL,19,Fcandidacy was announced, suggesting
OL,20,Fshe was the only name put forward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
