OL,3,CCouncil leader revealed as Labour
OL,4,Ccandidate for mayoral by-election
OL,6,FTwo other political parties have
OL,7,Fannounced their candidates for the
OL,8,Fmayoral race.
OL,10,FThe vote will take place on 30 July
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FThe successful candidate will hold
OL,14,Foffice until the next scheduled
OL,15,Felection for the mayoralty in May 2028.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
